snippet.title: The Wonderful 101: Remastered - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Originally released for the Nintendo Wii U in 2013, The Wonderful 101 returns powered up as The Wonderful 101: Remastered, available now on the Nintendo Switch eShop, with the disc version available in stores on June 30th! Now available for pre-order at all major retailers!

Get it here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/the-wonderful-101-remastered-switch/

#TheWonderful101 #TW101 #NintendoSwitch
